(44, 14, 23, 55, 2, 2, 2, 'ordained them elders in every church', 'Leadership and Teaching in the Church', 'This connection highlights the importance of establishing leaders in the church and the responsibility of those leaders to teach others. Both passages emphasize the commitment to faithful individuals who can continue the work of ministry.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
